{
  "verses": [
    {
      "verse_num": "1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh reigns! Let the earth rejoice!"
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Let the multitude of islands be glad!"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "2",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Clouds and darkness are around him. Righteousness and justice are the foundation of his throne."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "3",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "A fire goes before him, and burns up his adversaries on every side."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "4",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "His lightning lights up the world. The earth sees, and trembles."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "5",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The mountains melt like wax at the presence of Yahweh, at the presence of the Lord of the whole earth."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "6",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The heavens declare his righteousness. All the peoples have seen his glory."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "7",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Let all them be shamed who serve engraved images, who boast in their idols."
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Worship him, all you gods! [^35]"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "8",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Zion heard and was glad. The daughters of Judah rejoiced"
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "because of your judgments, Yahweh."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "9",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "For you, Yahweh, are most high above all the earth. You are exalted far above all gods."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "10",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "You who love Yahweh, hate evil! He preserves the souls of his saints."
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "He delivers them out of the hand of the wicked."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "11",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Light is sown for the righteous, and gladness for the upright in heart."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "12",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Be glad in Yahweh, you righteous people! Give thanks to his holy Name."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    }
  ]
}